title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1993-09-22
lineage: MAD > Sony D8 > Optical out > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab 1644 > CD-Wave > TLH > FLAC 1644 tagged. Recording & transfer by Andrew F.
description:
Set 1

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower, Minglewood Blues, Ramble On Rose, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Bird Song

Set 2

Easy Answers, Lazy River Road, Estimated Prophet-> Dark Star-> Drums-> Space-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Turn On Your Love Light*, E: I Fought The Law*

David Murray on sax during Birdsong and entire second set, * w/ James Cotton on harmonica
